# 01 | The Problem

## Event Planning is Broken

Planning a premium event today means:

- **Weeks of Google searches** to find the right caterer, venue, or photographer
- **Dozens of scattered emails** to get quotes, availability, and contracts
- **Zero price transparency** — vendors quote differently every time
- **No secure payment or escrow** — planners pay deposits over Venmo with no protection
- **13–15 vendors per event** — all coordinated through text messages and spreadsheets

> *"76% of event planners cite last-minute vendor issues as their single biggest stress point."*
> — Industry Survey, 2024

**The event industry generates $1.25 trillion globally — yet it runs on email and WhatsApp.**

---

# 02 | The Solution

## Introducing Eventore

**Eventore is the premium two-sided marketplace where event planners discover, book, and pay vetted vendors — all in one place.**

Think of us as the **"Airbnb for Event Vendors"** — a transparent, secure marketplace that brings the entire event ecosystem to a single, elegant dashboard.

### For Planners
- 🔍 **Discover** venues, caterers, photographers, DJs, and more in one platform
- 📍 **Map View** — find all available vendors near your event location
- 💬 **Secure Messaging** — inquire, negotiate, and confirm with contact-masking protection
- 💳 **Escrow Payments** — pay safely; funds released only after your event
- 📅 **Day-of Timeline** — manage your entire event day from the app

### For Vendors
- 🏪 **Professional Storefront** — showcase your portfolio, packages, and pricing
- 📩 **Inquiry Management** — receive and respond to leads in real-time
- 💰 **Instant Payouts** — receive funds 48 hours after event completion via Stripe
- ⭐ **Verified Reviews** — build a reputation that drives more bookings
- 📊 **Dashboard Analytics** — track views, inquiries, and revenue

