### North America Focus
- **38% of global events spend** originates in North America
- **2+ million weddings per year** in the United States alone
- **Average wedding cost: $33,000–$35,000** with 13–15 vendors per event
- **155,800 professional event planners** (BLS 2024) — not counting 2M+ freelancers
