### Technology Stack
- **Frontend:** React (Web PWA) + React Native / Expo (iOS & Android)
- **Backend:** Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Realtime, Storage)
- **Payments:** Stripe Connect (escrow + direct payouts)
- **Notifications:** Expo Push + Web Push API
- **Hosting:** Vercel (Web) + Expo EAS (Native)

