# 05 | Business Model

![Revenue Model](file:///C:/Users/rudra/.gemini/antigravity/brain/843a648c-0c1f-4b8e-9ac5-07bc44b6fa2a/revenue_model_slide_1780163466727.png)

## Three Diversified Revenue Streams

### Stream 1: Transaction Fee (Core)
> **8% platform fee on every confirmed booking**

- Planner pays the full amount → Eventore takes 8% → Vendor receives 92%
- Average wedding vendor booking: ~$2,500 → **$200 per booking**
- A typical wedding with 13 vendors = **$2,600+ GMV per event**
- Scales entirely with platform usage — zero marginal cost

### Stream 2: Vendor Pro Subscriptions
> **$29/month or $249/year per vendor**

- Priority placement in search results
- Analytics dashboard (views, conversion rate, revenue tracking)
- Unlimited portfolio uploads
- "Pro" badge on profile

### Stream 3: Premium Listing Boosts
> **$49–$149 per boost campaign**

- Featured placement on the Discover map for 7 days
- "Sponsored" category card on the homepage
- Push notification to planners in the vendor's city

