# 08 | Go-To-Market Strategy

## Three Channels, One Flywheel

### Channel 1: Vendor-Led Growth (Supply Side)
1. Personally onboard first 100 vendors in Vancouver (done via Instagram outreach + cold email)
2. Offer first 3 months free → convert to $29/month subscription
3. Vendors promote their Eventore profile to their own client networks
4. Each vendor brings average of 8–15 potential planners to the platform

### Channel 2: Creator & Influencer Partnerships
1. Partner with top wedding and event content creators on Instagram and TikTok
2. Sponsored posts to planner and couple audiences
3. Co-created content (real planning journeys using the app)
4. Budget: $5,000/month in Year 1 influencer spend

### Channel 3: SEO & Content Marketing
1. "Best [vendor category] in [city]" landing pages — high-intent search traffic
2. Blog: event planning tips, vendor guides, budgeting tools
3. Long-tail local SEO targeting 500+ city/category combinations
4. Expected: 15,000 monthly organic visitors by Month 12

