# 11 | Vision

## The Future of the Events Economy

> *"In 5 years, every wedding planner in Canada will start their vendor search on Eventore — the same way every traveler starts with Airbnb."*

### Year 3 Roadmap
- 🌎 Expand to 20 major North American cities
- 🤖 AI-powered vendor matching (event type + cultural preferences + budget = instant shortlist)
- 🏆 Eventore Verified — premium background-checked vendor tier
- 📊 Vendor analytics suite — conversion tracking, revenue insights, competitor benchmarking
- 💼 Eventore for Enterprises — corporate event management dashboard for SMBs

### Why Now?
- Post-pandemic events industry **rebounded 122%** from 2022 to 2024
- **Gen Z and Millennial couples** (primary market) are digital-first and expect marketplace-grade experiences
- **AI tailwinds** making personalization and vendor matching dramatically cheaper to build
- **No dominant marketplace player** has emerged — the market is waiting for Eventore

